Please replace pdfsam-win32inst-v0_6_sr3.exe with the original installer you may 
found on: http://sourceforge.net/projects/pdfsam/

Version: 0.6 sr 3
Installed-Size: 2.8 Mo
Description: pdfsam is an open source tool (GPL license) designed to handle 
pdf files. It requiers a Java Virtual Machine 1.4.2 or higher and it’s released
in 2 versions, basic and enhanced.

Source: http://sourceforge.net/projects/pdfsam/

The file "installpdfsam.bat" is useful of executable "shortcut.exe", to 
create shortcuts.
Source: http://www.optimumx.com/download/#Shortcut